<li>Since the conditions of growth that minimize Dp also maximize hya expression , it is plausible that the hya response to pHe is at least partially mediated by ArcA .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=10464194" target="_blank">10464194</a>]<br></li>
