<li>In vitro studies with the sodA promoter , including footprinting experiments , suggest that ArcA binds to DNA in an oligomeric form ( Tardat and Touati , 1993 ) .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=8022271" target="_blank">8022271</a>]<br></li>
