<li>Conclusion In this , our fourth study of global gene-expression profiling in E. coli K12 , we have again employed rigorous statistical treatment of the data to infer differential expression for 1139 genes in the presence and absence of the ArcA regulatory protein .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=15699038" target="_blank">15699038</a>]<br></li>
