<li>Regulation of the Puu pathway by PuuR seems to be a simple , primary regulatory system that maintains the putrescine concentration in the cell , although there is a possibility of other regulatory mechanisms such as an aeration shift by FNR or ArcA for expression of the Puu pathway ( 14 ) .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=22522900" target="_blank">22522900</a>]<br></li>
